{"word":"ἅρπη","slug":"ἅρπη","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἅρπη</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:vide'>v.</a> <a href='S:ἁρπάζω'><el>ἁρπάζω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b>a bird of prey, <i>a kite</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a sickle</i>, = <a href='S:δρέπανον'><el>δρέπανον</el></a>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}